title: JSTrojanDownloaderNemucod
extract: JS/Nemucod is a JavaScript downloader trojan that targets users through malware spam campaigns. JS/Nemucod downloads additional malware and executes it without the user's consent. JS/Nemucod usually arrives on an infected machine through malicious spam emails with .zip extensions.Jun 22, 2018
